---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof vs EmbedReviews — Social Proof Widget Comparison | SocialProof" description="EmbedReviews aggregates third-party review platform data. SocialProof collects direct testimonials from your customers. Compare pricing, features, and use cases." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/vs/embedreviews">
<style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #fff; color: #111; }
    nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    nav a.logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #111; text-decoration: none; }
    nav .nav-links a { margin-left: 1.5rem; color: #555; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    nav .cta-nav { background: #111; color: #fff !important; padding: 0.45rem 1rem; border-radius: 6px; }
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .vs-badge { display: inline-block; background: #f0f0f0; color: #555; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: .35rem .75rem; border-radius: 99px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .hero h1 span { color: #4f46e5; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; color: #444; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
    .hero-cta { display: inline-block; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    .hero-cta:hover { background: #3730a3; }
    section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .compare-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .compare-table th { padding: .75rem 1rem; text-align: left; font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em; color: #888; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; }
    .compare-table th:nth-child(2) { color: #4f46e5; }
    .compare-table td { padding: .85rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; font-size: 0.97rem; vertical-align: top; }
    .compare-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .compare-table td:first-child { color: #555; font-weight: 500; }
    .yes { color: #16a34a; font-weight: 600; }
    .no { color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600; }
    .partial { color: #d97706; font-weight: 600; }
    .key-diff { background: #f8f7ff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .key-diff h3 { margin: 0 0 1rem; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .key-diff p { color: #555; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .key-diff p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .use-case-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    @media (max-width: 600px) { .use-case-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    .use-case-card { border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 10px; padding: 1.5rem; }
    .use-case-card h3 { margin: 0 0 .75rem; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .use-case-card ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; color: #555; font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.7; }
    .cta-section { background: #111; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem; margin-top: 3rem; }
    .cta-section h2 { color: #fff; }
    .cta-section p { color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .cta-section a { background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    footer { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; color: #888; font-size: 0.85rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
    footer a { color: #888; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 .75rem; }
</style>

<nav>
  <a href="/" class="logo">SocialProof</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/vs/">Comparisons</a>
    <a href="/#pricing">Pricing</a>
    <a href="/app/signup" class="cta-nav">Try free</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="vs-badge">SocialProof vs EmbedReviews</div>
  <h1>Aggregate third-party reviews<br/>or <span>collect your own?</span></h1>
  <p>EmbedReviews pulls in reviews from Google, Facebook, and other platforms and displays them as a widget. SocialProof collects direct testimonials from customers without requiring review platforms. Different tools for different needs.</p>
  <a href="/app/signup" class="hero-cta">Try SocialProof free — no credit card</a>
</div>

<section>
  <div class="key-diff">
    <h3>The fundamental difference</h3>
    <p><strong>EmbedReviews</strong> is a review aggregator. It connects to your Google Business Profile, Facebook Page, Yelp, and other platforms and pulls those reviews into a widget for your site. If you already have reviews on those platforms and want to display them on your website, EmbedReviews solves that problem.</p>
    <p><strong>SocialProof</strong> is a testimonial collector. You send customers a link, they write their testimonial directly, you approve it, and it appears on your site. You're not dependent on any third-party platform. Customers don't need a Google account, Yelp account, or Facebook account to leave a testimonial.</p>
    <p>If you have existing Google reviews you want to showcase: EmbedReviews is built for that. If you want to collect <em>new</em> testimonials from customers who don't use review platforms, or if you want testimonials that are more detailed and personal than a typical Google review: that's SocialProof's strength.</p>
  </div>

  <h2>Side-by-side comparison</h2>
  <table class="compare-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Feature</th>
        <th>SocialProof</th>
        <th>EmbedReviews</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Starting price</td>
        <td class="yes">Free forever (1 widget)</td>
        <td class="partial">~$29/month</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Collect direct testimonials (no review platform)</td>
        <td class="yes">Yes — core feature</td>
        <td class="no">No</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Aggregate Google / Facebook reviews</td>
        <td class="no">No</td>
        <td class="yes">Yes — core feature</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Customer needs Google/Facebook account</td>
        <td class="yes">No — direct link</td>
        <td class="no">Yes — to leave original reviews</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Approval workflow (choose what displays)</td>
        <td class="yes">Yes — full control</td>
        <td class="partial">Limited filtering only</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Works for businesses with no Google presence</td>
        <td class="yes">Yes</td>
        <td class="no">No — requires connected accounts</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Setup time</td>
        <td class="yes">5 minutes</td>
        <td class="partial">30-60 min (account connections)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Testimonials are yours (not platform-dependent)</td>
        <td class="yes">Yes — you own them</td>
        <td class="no">No — depends on platform APIs</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Who should use which tool?</h2>
  <div class="use-case-grid">
    <div class="use-case-card">
      <h3>✅ Pick SocialProof if you…</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Want to collect new testimonials directly from customers</li>
        <li>Serve customers who don't have Google/Yelp accounts</li>
        <li>Run a B2B or professional services business</li>
        <li>Want full control over every word that appears on your site</li>
        <li>Don't want to depend on third-party platform API uptime</li>
        <li>Are starting out and have few or no existing platform reviews</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="use-case-card">
      <h3>✅ Pick EmbedReviews if you…</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Already have a strong Google Business Profile with many reviews</li>
        <li>Want to display existing third-party reviews on your site</li>
        <li>Run a local business where Google reviews are the gold standard</li>
        <li>Need to pull from multiple platforms (Google + Facebook + Yelp) into one widget</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="cta-section">
  <h2>Collect testimonials without review platforms.</h2>
  <p>Free to start. Your customers submit directly. You approve and display. No Google account required.</p>
  <a href="/app/signup">Try SocialProof free →</a>
</div>

<footer>
  <a href="/">SocialProof</a>
  <a href="/vs/">All comparisons</a>
  <a href="/#pricing">Pricing</a>
  <a href="/app/signup">Sign up free</a>
</footer>

<div class="footer-links" style="margin-top:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;font-size:0.9rem;">
  <strong style="color:#374151;">Also explore:</strong>
  <a href="/for/coaches" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Coaches</a>
  <a href="/for/freelancers" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Freelancers</a>
  <a href="/for/ecommerce" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Ecommerce</a>
  <a href="/vs/senja" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Senja</a>
  <a href="/vs/testimonial" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Testimonial.to</a>
</div>
</Base>
